item.title: About
item.dc:creator: rrohitttt
item.content:encoded:
Rohit, Lakshana and Raveena are students currently pursuing their Bachelors in Electronics and Computer Science.

We aspire to create solutions with the learning and implication of evolving technology. We went from staring blankly into their laptop screens most of the time, to learning and growing our productivity.

Job hunting, keeping up with trends with respect to investments is one of the difficult things to get through especially as a beginner. So, we have com forward with the idea of integrating different services and websites to make it easy for a beginner to surf through and get a understanding.

Lakshana K

COO, Operations Lead

"The downside of surplus data on hands to work with, often leads to no work being done. So trying to make things and data simpler."

Rohit T

CEO, Technical Lead

"I take pride in saying that I've strike a delicate balance between my work and personal life, in order to expand my horizons."

G. Raveena

Marketing Head

"As good as technical solutions are, they still need to sold to common people in simpler and creative ways, I do exactly that."

item.title: Episode 3: A Cycle of Emotions
item.dc:creator: rrohitttt
item.content:encoded:
Quadrat is a weekly podcast where we discuss all things related to womanhood, from fundamental rights to feminism, body literacy and mental health. We hope to help women become more empowered through knowledge and information, whether they're in America, Africa or in the Middle East.

Join us every week!

“Do we need periods if they make us crazy?”, Sarah asks. Hint: yes, we do. We reached out to our friend Diana Roth, an endocrinologist specialised in women’s hormonal health to know how menstrual cycles impact women’s brains and emotions.

item.title: Home
item.dc:creator: rrohitttt
item.content:encoded:
Job hunting to riding trend waves. Here's your one-stop to all your queries and trends.

#OneStopSolution

Internships and Job Opportunities:

Internships are very hard to find as a student and confusing to approach. So, We have provided with a link that is updated every 24 hours with latest openings. You can Click here to have a look.

Click here

As important as it is to find the openings for a position, it is just as important to know how to crack various interviews and bootstrap your skills. For which, We have written a detailed walkthrough you can refer to by Clicking here.

Click here

Does getting a job consolidate one's life? Make us financially independent?

The answer to it is a Resounding NOOOOO! If the goal behind getting a job is to make money so to be "financial free", it is a absolute joke in my opinion. Half of millennials are not sure what financial independence really even means. But, No worries as we have you covered in that case too. We have a series of educational driven purpose articles which are personal finance and wealth growth oriented.

I believe it is just as important to learn to manage your finances as important as it is to have a sustainable job. Here's an article where i walk you through how investing and personal finance has practically changed lifestyles and means of living.

Article

Here are some articles to educate you upon various aspects:

Article 1: How Web 3.0 can and will impact higher education.

The article here talks about the potential web 3.0 carries with it and how it can and will impact the traditional educational system for the better. Not just the student but institutions to make use of it.

The Subtle art of cracking interviews with Soft Skills

Bootstrapping yourself with skills only takes you so far, I firmly believe and advocate that Soft skills and technical communications are which take you forward in career or in any interview.

Click here

In the above linked article, we speak about how important role soft skills play in cracking your dream job's interview and overall contributes to your career success.

"In investing what is comfortable is rarely profitable."

While investing is fundamental for wealth growth, It is not everyone's bread and butter. At the same time, Trading is not as simple or humanly predictable. The best solution to this is "Trading bots"

Click Here

The above article speaks to the solution I have introduced. It speaks about what trading bots are, How they work and how you as a complete beginner can take advantage of them and make bucks.
